GlobalVariables.StudyDescription: SDTM datasets built from CDASH datasets

ItemGroupDef.Name: CM
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per recorded medication occurrence or constant-dosing interval per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: EX
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per constant dosing interval per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: AE
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per adverse event per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: DS
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per disposition status or protocol milestone per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: MH
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per medical history event per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: LB
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per analyte per planned time point number per time point reference per visit per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: QS
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per questionnaire per question per time point per visit per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: SC
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per characteristic per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: VS
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per vital sign measurement per time point per visit per subject

ItemGroupDef.Name: SUPPDS
ItemGroupDef.def:Structure: One record per IDVAR, IDVARVAL, and QNAM value per subject

Obtain the highest CDASH.EX.EXDSTXT value for each subject: If the highest value of CDASH.EX.EXDSTXT is '81' then SDTM.DM.ACTARMCD='Xan_Hi', else if the highest value of CDASH.EX.EXDSTXT is '54' then SDTM.DM.ACTARMCD='Xan_Lo', else if the highest value of CDASH.EX.EXDSTXT is '0' then SDTM.DM.ACTARMCD='Pbo'. If CDASH.X1.ARM='Scrnfail' then SDTM.DM.ACTARMCD='Scrnfail'
CDASH.AE.AEENDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.AE.AEENDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC - only calculate when CDASH.AE.AEENDAT is a complete date, null when it is a partial date
When CDASH.AE.AESER='No' then SDTM.AE.AESER='N', else SDTM.AE.AESER='Y' when CDASH.AE.AESER in ('1','2','3','4','5','6','7','8')
CDASH.AE.AESTDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.AE.AESTDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC - only calculate when CDASH.AE.AESTDAT is a complete date, null when it is a partial date
CDASH.CM.CMENDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.CM.CMENDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC - only calculate when CDASH.CM.CMENDAT is a complete date, null when it is a partial date
CDASH.CM.CMSTDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.CM.CMSTDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC - only calculate when CDASH.CM.CMSTDAT is a complete date, null when it is a partial date
CDASH.DM.DMDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.DM.DMDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC

SDTM.DS.DSCAT=CDASH.DS.DSCAT and add derived records for SDTM.DS.DSDECOD="FINAL LAB VISIT" by selecting last visit present in SDTM.LB, set SDTM.DS.DSCAT to 'OTHER EVENT' for these added derived records.
SDTM.DS.DSDECOD=CDASH.DS.DSDECOD and add derived records for SDTM.DS.DSDECOD="FINAL LAB VISIT" by selecting last visit present in SDTM.LB
CDASH.DS.DSSTDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.DS.DSSTDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC
SDTM.DS.DSTERM=CDASH.DS.DSTERM and add derived records for SDTM.DS.DSTERM="FINAL LAB VISIT" by selecting last visit present in SDTM.LB
CDASH.LB.LBDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.LB.LBDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC
CDASH.MH.MHDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.MH.MHDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC
If CDASH.MH.MHSEV=1 then SDTM.MH.MHSEV='MILD' else if CDASH.MH.MHSEV=2 then SDTM.MH.MHSEV='MODERATE' else if CDASH.MH.MHSEV=3 then SDTM.MH.MHSEV='SEVERE' else SDTM.MH.MHSEV is null
CDASH.QS.QSDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.QS.QSDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC

Re-derive SDTM.QS.QSSTRESN values for SDTM.QS.QSTESTCD in ('ACTOT','NPTOT') in accordance with SAP Appendix 1 scoring instructions; For all other parameters SDTM.QS.QSSTRESN=SDTM.QS.QSSTRESC converted to numeric;
CDASH.SC.SCDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.SC.SCDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC
Derived as last two characters from CDASH.<DOMAIN>.STUDYID contatenated with CDASH.<DOMAIN>.SITEID and CDASH.<DOMAIN>.SUBJID separated by a '-'
CDASH.VS.VSDAT minus (date portion of SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC) , add 1 if CDASH.VS.VSDAT >= SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC
AEACN=Null (data on action taken concerning study treatment was not collected)
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
CDASH.DS.DTHDAT when CDASH.DS.DSTERM='DEATH' converted to IS08601 format
If SDTM.DM.DTHDTC is not null then SDTM.DM.DTHFL='Y'
Latest CDASH.DS.DSDAT date available from CDASH.DS where CDASH.DS.DSCAT='DISPOSITION EVENT' per subject converted to IS08601 format. Only populated when SDTM.DM.RFSTDTC is not null.
Date of informed consent was not entered in database (see annotated CRF)
CDASH.X1.RFPENDAT and CDASH.X1.RFPENTIM converted to IS08601 format
CDASH.EX.EXSTDAT where CDASH.EX.VISIT='BASELINE' converted to IS08601 format
Latest CDASH.EX.EXENDAT date available from CDASH.EX per subject converted to IS08601 format
CDASH.EX.EXSTDAT where CDASH.EX.VISIT='BASELINE' converted to IS08601 format
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
SDTM.LB.LBDTC is comprised of CDASH.LB.LBDAT and CDASH.LB.LBTIM converted to ISO8601 format

If SDTM.LB.LBSTRESN > SDTM.LB.LBSTNRHI then SDTM.LB.LBNRIND="HIGH", else if SDTM.LB.LBSTRESN < SDTM.LB.LBSTNRLO then LBNRIND="LOW". If SDTM.LB.LBSTRESN between SDTM.LB.LBSTNRLO and SDTM.LB.LBSTNRHI then SDTM.LB.LBNRIND="NORMAL". Selected urinalysis parameters (e.g. Ketones) are classified as NORMAL or ABNORMAL only.
CDASH.LB.LBORNRHI converted to numeric variable standard unit
CDASH.LB.LBORNRLO converted to a numeric variable standard unit
SDTM.LB.LBSTRESC converted to a numeric variable
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
if SDTM.QS.QSTESTCD in ('ACTOT' 'NPTOT') or if the eight character of SDTM.QS.QSTESTCD='S' then SDTM.QS.QSDRVFL='Y'
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID
CDASH.SC.EDLEVEL_SCORRES converted to a numeric variable
Extract first 2 chars from first word in SDTM.SC.SCTEST concatenated with the second word in SDTM.SC.SCTEST
Set to value of parent SDTM.DS.DSSEQ where SDTM.DS.DSTERM='PROTOCOL ENTRY CRITERIA NOT MET'
Set to value of parent SDTM.DS.DSTERM where SDTM.DS.DSTERM='PROTOCOL ENTRY CRITERIA NOT MET'
Extract last 2 numbers from CDASH.IE.IETESTCD value

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSDAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSDAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSDAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSDAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSDAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSDTC=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSDAT
If SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM="815" then SDTM.VS.VSELTM="PT5M" else if SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM="816" then SDTM.VS.VSELTM="PT1M" else if SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM="817" then SDTM.VS.VSELTM="PT3M"

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRES=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSORRES

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSORRESU=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSORRESU

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSPOS=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSPOS else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSPOS=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSPOS else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSPOS=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSPOS
Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSSTAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSSTAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSSTAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSSTAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSSTAT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTAT=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSSTAT

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSORRES else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSORRES converted to centimetres to 2 d.p. else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSORRES*0.4536 (converted to kilograms) to 2 d.p. else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESC=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSORRES converted to degrees celsius to 2 d.p.

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSORRES converted to numeric else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSORRES converted to numeric else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSORRES converted to numeric else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.HEIGHT_VSORRES converted to centimetres to 2 d.p. and numeric else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.WEIGHT_VSORRES*0.4536 (converted to kilograms) to 2 d.p. and numeric else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESN=CDASH.VS.TEMP_VSORRES converted to degrees celsius to 2 d.p. and numeric

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSORRESU else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="HEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU="cm" else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="WEIGHT" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU="kg" else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="TEMP" then SDTM.VS.VSSTRESU="C"

SDTM.VS.VSTEST='Diastolic Blood Pressure' when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='DIABP' SDTM.VS.VSTEST="Systolic Blood Pressure" when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='SYSBP' SDTM.VS.VSTEST="Pulse Rate" when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='PULSE' SDTM.VS.VSTEST="Height" when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='HEIGHT' SDTM.VS.VSTEST="Weight" when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='WEIGHT' SDTM.VS.VSTEST="Temperature" when SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='TEMP'

SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='DIABP' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.DIABP_xxx variables SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='SYSBP' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.SYSBP_xxx variables SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='PULSE' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.PULSE_xxx variables SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='WEIGHT' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.WEIGHT_xxx variables SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='HEIGHT' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.HEIGHT_xxx variables SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD='TEMP' when SDTM record variable values originate from CDASH.TEMP_xxx variables

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPT=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSTPT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPT=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSTPT else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSTPT=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSTPT

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM=CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSTPTNUM else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM=CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSTPTNUM else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTNUM=CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSTPTNUM

If SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="DIABP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTREF="PATIENT" concatenated to CDASH.VS.DIABP_VSPOS else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="SYSBP" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTREF="PATIENT" concatenated to CDASH.VS.SYSBP_VSPOS else if SDTM.VS.VSTESTCD="PULSE" then SDTM.VS.VSTPTREF="PATIENT" concatenated to CDASH.VS.PULSE_VSPOS
